    "那如果我这么做呢？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5027
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_948e6cf8:

    # "The small kiss I place on her thigh is enough to make Rin lose her composure, to shut her eyes, to squeal almost inaudibly."
    "我在琳的大腿上微微吻了一下，这已经足够打破她的镇定了，她闭上了眼睛，几乎不可闻地尖叫一声。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5029
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7ff3e211:

    # "…Is that what you want too? Would it be all right now? To take this step?"
    "……你也想要这个吗？现在已经没关系了么？我们可以走下这一步？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5034
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a28d4e58:

