# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5036
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_90e71c6b:

    # "Hazy thoughts float somewhere in the back of my unfocused mind."
    "在我无法集中注意的脑海中，朦胧模糊的思绪飘浮在后方的某处。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5038
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_fb1d0adc:

    # "Somehow, this whole situation is making it hard to think, as if my head was full of cotton fluff."
    "整个情形让我有些难以思考，像是我的脑袋里塞满了毛绒绒的棉花一般。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5040
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_0013710b:

    # "But that's all right. It seems thinking is not something we need right now."
    "不过没关系。看起来思考不是我们现在需要的东西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5048
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d29c8be8:

