    "我只是把它们从她身体中释放出来了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5081
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ac55072a:

    # "She becomes more and more moist, and I drink from her, feeling a heat growing inside myself."
    "她变得越来越湿，我喝着她的津液，感到一股热浪在自己的体内缓缓上涨。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5083
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_771e8784:

    # "I try to reach her deepest places, to feel all of her I can this way."
    "我试图探向她的最深处，感受着自己能接触到她的每个角落，她的全部。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5085
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2fcdd301:

    # "My every action is met with a different reaction, but all of those are out of pure lust."
    "我的每个举动都会激起一种不同的反应，但在它们所有的源头，都是纯粹的情欲。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5090
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c1eb7555:

    # "Rin is lost in desire, willing to let anything happen to her if I do it right now."
    "琳迷失在了欲望之中，愿意放开一切，不论我现在对她做什么。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5092
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_655194e7:

    # "She becomes closer and closer to the moment of release, but the way to that is an uphill slope of madness."
    "她离那个释放的瞬间越来越近，但是攀向巅峰的路途是一道峭壁，由疯狂铸成。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5094
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2197b35b:

    # "Still, she is going that way."
    "然而，她却依旧向着那个点奔去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5096
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f4c46b9c:

    # "The muscles don't relax any more between the waves of ecstatic spasms."
    "在一波波意乱神迷的痉挛间，她的肌肉再也没有放松下来。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5098
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4f0d3e48:

    # "Rin just becomes tenser and tenser, contracting so much that it must be physically painful, but I do not let go."
    "琳绷得越来越紧，一次又一次收缩着，剧烈得一定让她痛苦，但是我没有放开。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5100
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_835d7633:

    # "I keep going, and I know she wants it too, she desperately wants me to do this to her."
    "我继续下去，明白她也在如此渴望，她正绝望地盼着我对她这么做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5102
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d98c2bb1:

    # "A leg curls around my shoulders and draws me closer, so close that I think that I'm going to choke."
    "一条腿绕过了我的肩膀，把我拉得更近，近得我觉得自己都要窒息了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5104
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_aa67e94a:

    # "I keep going because it's the only possibility."
    "我依然继续着，因为除此之外别无可能。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5109
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_6c2ad772:

    # "As I push the button that drives her into gasping for breath, locking her leg into a cramp against my back, losing her mind in the sensation, at that precise moment I seem to forget all that was meant to be, all that should be."
    "我终于把她逼过了那个点，让她喘息着，犹如在渴求空气，她把腿在一阵痉挛中死死地锁在了我的背后，在这道极乐中瓦解了理智，就在同一瞬间，我似乎忘掉了世间万物所有的意义，所有的目的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5111
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_211c2fad:

    # "All I know is that she came here and… I think there was a towel at some point, too."
    "我只记得她来到这里，然后……我想在某个时刻还出现了一条毛巾。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5113
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_5f33fb7a:

    # "None of it matters, all that matters is this, what we have now."
    "都不重要了，重要的只是这个，我们之间正拥有的这些。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5115
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b83a7f06:

    # "Her orgasm surges through me too, exciting me in a completely new way."
    "她的高潮也涌过了我，以一种全新的方式刺激着我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5117
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a054b289:

    # "It makes me feel anxious, nervous. Bothered."
    "让我感觉不安，紧张。担心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5123
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_db0d05ee:

    # "As her body relaxes, I try to kiss her down there again, but it startles her, causing her to jump."
    "随着她的身体放松下来，我试图再次去吻那下面，不过她被吓到了，让她惊了一跳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5128
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f563d778:

    # rin "No… Hisao… Enough."
    rin "别……久夫……够了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5130
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_03987e9d:

    # rin "Come here."
    rin "过来。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5135
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1e2eef89:

    # "I stand up to remove the last piece of clothing Rin has."
    "我站起身，移走琳身上的最后一件衣服。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5137
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1539ab33:

    # "She leans against me to catch her breath, tickling me with warm air exhaled into my shirt."
    "她靠在我身上，想要让呼吸平稳下来，她温暖的气息钻进了我的衬衫里，挠痒了我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5139
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_428c5dfb:

    # "Blindly, I reach behind her back to feel my way below her shoulder blades, to find the contraption that fastens her bra."
    "我盲目地把手伸到了她的背后，在她的肩胛骨下摸索着，想要找到那个将她的胸罩系在一起的扣件。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5141
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2d295887:

    # "It opens more easily than I thought, falling to the floor somewhere."
    "它比我预期中更轻易地打开了，落到了地上的某处。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5150
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4232dc2a:

    # "Her bare skin against me is a sensation so wonderful that I want to have more of it, and I do, embracing her."
    "她赤裸的肌肤贴着我的感觉实在是太美妙了，让我只想尝到更多，我也确实那么做了，抱住了她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5152
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_dcc1063d:

    # "Rin's hair smells of rain, and I realize that I'm not hearing the sound of rainfall any more."
    "琳的头发带着雨水的气息，我发现自己已经听不见雨落声了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5154
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_fc569c5d:

    # "It's a sobering thing. The cushion that enveloped us into a reality of our own is now gone, and I realize more clearly what is happening."
    "像是正在清醒的过程中。那些将我们包裹进一个只属于我们的现实中的垫子已经消失了，我更加清晰地意识到了正在发生什么。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5159
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4bd05e8c:

    # hi "You know, this really is not what friends should be doing."
    hi "嗯，你看，这真的不是朋友间该做的事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5161
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d6494819:

    # "I whisper, once again noticing how such a simple matter as talking can be overbearingly difficult at times."
    "我对她低语道，再次发现有时就连像说话这样简单的事也会变得无比困难。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5166
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d816abff:

    # rin "Will you stop being my friend?"
    rin "你不准备继续做我的朋友了吗？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5168
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_deb37c77:

    # "That wasn't what I meant, but her serious tone and the layers of connotations behind Rin's question give me pause."
    "我不是这个意思，不过琳的语气非常严肃，而且这问题下一层层的涵义让我不由得犹豫了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5173
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_974c322b:

    # hi "Nah."
    hi "没，不会的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5178
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2559cfc1:

    # rin "I… think it might be all right. Even if you did."
    rin "我……我觉得可能会没关系的。就算你不准备了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5180
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_008c6c91:

    # "I hug her and smile into her hair, understanding Rin perfectly for once."
    "我将她搂向怀抱，对着她的头发笑了，这一次我彻底地理解了琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5185
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_666c25bb:

    # rin "You are wet."
    rin "你都湿了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5187
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_0571641c:

    # "The remnants of water on her skin have drained into my shirt."
    "她皮肤上残留的雨水浸进了我的衬衫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5189
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_6683f306:

    # "Somehow, even her statements of the obvious make me glad right now."
    "不知为何，就算她那些不言而喻的陈述也让我感到欣慰。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5194
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7027cd75:

    # hi "You're right. I am. But that's your fault."
    hi "没错，确实。不过这是你的错。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5199
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_350e4c5d:

    # rin "I want to see you."
    rin "我想看看你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5206
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_21881e75:

    # "I comply, standing back to open the buttons of my shirt, much more quickly than when I undid Rin's buttons."
    "我遵从了，退开来解开自己衬衫的纽扣，比我为琳脱衣时要快得多。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5208
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2d91b7ea:

    # "A sudden sense of haste strikes me, spurring me to rush forward."
    "忽然间，我感觉急切起来，想要立刻继续下去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5210
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_435c8b50:

    # "Every second I'm not touching Rin is a second wasted, a chance lost."
    "我没有与琳接触的每一秒钟都是被浪费掉的，都是一个被荒废的机会。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5212
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_733ce239:

    # "My belt buckle proves an obstacle despite my ability to open it in an eyeblink under normal circumstances."
    "我的皮带扣变成了一道障碍，虽然在平时，我在眨眼之间就能打开它。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5217
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c415f634:

    # "While I fumble with it, I don't notice Rin bringing her foot up between us until she starts tracing my chest with her toe."
    "我捣弄着它，没有注意到琳把脚抬到了我们之间，直到她开始用脚趾在我的胸前描画。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5222
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ee0d6ee6:

    # "I look down to see what she's looking at…"
    "我低头去看她正在看什么……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5224
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f8375736:

    # hi "My heart…"
    hi "我的心脏……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5226
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e3509c53:

    # "I reflexively flinch back, covering the scar tissue in the middle of my chest."
    "我条件反射般地畏缩了一下，遮住了胸口正中央的疤痕。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5228
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_875587e7:

    # "The shallow mark that the surgery following my heart attack left on my body has healed already but… well, it's not a particularly pretty sight if not overly repulsive either."
    "那次我心脏病发作后的手术疤痕还留在那里，很浅，已经愈合了，可是……好吧，那不是什么特别赏心悦目的景象，虽然也不是特别让人作呕。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5230
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_af71731a:

    # "It's barely noticeable, but she does have an eye for detail. Is this why she said she wanted to see me?"
    "它几乎难以察觉，但她确实擅于捕捉细节。这就是她说她想要看我的意思吗？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5232
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_718f6e3e:

    # "I had sorta forgotten about this because of all this mess with Rin, but now all the unpleasant things connected to my condition surface at once, rushing through my mind like a flash flood."
    "发生了这么多和琳有关的乱子，我都有些把它给忘了，可现在，所有那些与我的病相关的不愉快东西都一下子浮现出来，像是山洪暴发一样奔涌过我的脑海。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5234
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_fba91042:

    # "And oh God all the stories about old guys getting heart attacks when having sex, what if…"
    "还有，老天，还有所有那些老头们在性爱时心脏病发作的故事，万一……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5239
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_aa95e2ab:

    # rin "Hisao."
    rin "久夫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5241
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce617998_4:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5243
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8c1f9dd0:

    # "Realizing that I might just have spoiled the mood, I stumble to explain myself."
    "我意识到自己可能刚把气氛给毁了，连忙结结巴巴地开始解释。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5248
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_cd4cb466:

    # hi "Ah… sorry, it's just that…"
    hi "啊……抱歉，只是，那个……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5253
translate zh_hans a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2fda4de3:

